{"ID":"20260609125526-hwuku0j","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260609125526-hwuku0j","title":"2021年北京卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260609125617"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260609125541-gfw6gxj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125541-gfw6gxj","updated":"20260609125541"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"①近年来，我国数字经济欣欣向荣，互联网应用百花齐放。②"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"网络的发展便捷了人们的生活，与此同时"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，给管网治网带来了许多新的挑战。③目前各类服务端APP都上线了青少年模式，虽取得了一定成效，但仍存在不少漏洞。④"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"随着短视频、直播平台的异军突起，还带来了未成年人沉迷网络、打赏主播等问题，"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"引起家长的普遍担忧。⑤事实上，不仅未成年人需要清朗的网络环境，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"对广大人民群众而言，也渴求健康的网络空间"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。⑥网络上，水军、黑公关等顽瘴痼疾反复兴风作浪，淫秽色情、赌博诈骗信息屡禁不绝，群众对此反应强烈，普遍期待开展一场网络大扫除。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125526-plztt8h","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609125526-plztt8h","updated":"20260609125552"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260609125552-c9706z4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125552-c9706z4","updated":"20260609125552"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"(1)下列说法不正确的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609125552-a7ahnm7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125552-a7ahnm7","updated":"20260609125552"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．加点的两个四字成语使用得当。                    B．加波浪线的两句有相同的语病。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125552-tuqx9ag","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125552-tuqx9ag","updated":"20260609125552"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．第⑤⑥两句的位置不能够互换。                 D．末句的“反应”应改为“反映”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125552-14zht3r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125552-14zht3r","updated":"20260609125552"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"(2)不改变原意，将第②句中画线并被逗号隔开的两个语言片段整合为一个。将改写后的答案写在答题卡上。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125526-1cjqxvt","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609125526-1cjqxvt","updated":"20260609125604"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260609125604-41msgmq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125604-41msgmq","updated":"20260609125604"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"(1)D"}]},{"ID":"20260609125604-x5ea1q6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125604-x5ea1q6","updated":"20260609125604"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"(2)网络的发展在便捷了人们的生活的同时"}]},{"ID":"20260609125526-01e8474","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609125526-01e8474","updated":"20260609125617"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260609125617-tgjcuue","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125617-tgjcuue","updated":"20260609125617"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（1）本题考查学生语言表达之正确使用词语及辨析并修改病句的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125617-mkpkp9u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125617-mkpkp9u","updated":"20260609125617"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.百花齐放：不同形式和风格的各种艺术作品自由发展；形容艺术界的繁荣景象。此处形容应用风格不同，种类繁多，使用正确。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125617-ubmyv6x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125617-ubmyv6x","updated":"20260609125617"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兴风作浪：比喻制造事端，煽动别人起来捣乱。此处形容不法分子煽动他人情绪，使用正确。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125617-0nu71z5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125617-0nu71z5","updated":"20260609125617"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B.成分残缺，两句都存在滥用介词而导致句子缺乏主语的语病，第一句删掉“随着”，第二句删掉“对……而言”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125617-m0segix","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125617-m0segix","updated":"20260609125617"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.⑤句是原因，⑥句是结果，故二者不能互换正确。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125617-ae307qb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125617-ae307qb","updated":"20260609125617"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D.反应：机体受到体内或体外的刺激而引起相应的活动，事情所引起的意见、态度或行动等。反映：把情况或意见等向上级报告。此处群众的“反应”显然是指群众对这类情况的意见、态度，故使用正确，无须更改。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125617-xx9hxpl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125617-xx9hxpl","updated":"20260609125617"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选D。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125617-qvstpwg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125617-qvstpwg","updated":"20260609125617"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（2）本题考查学生变换句式的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125617-c9csbbh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125617-c9csbbh","updated":"20260609125617"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"把“与此同时”统合到前一句中，因为前句就是“此”，故需要去掉“与此”，换成“……的同时”。因“同时”是个时间词，故还应在前一句谓语前加上“在”字，将它变成时间状语，最终变换为“网络的发展在便捷了人们的生活的同时”。"}]}]}